name: Current Topics in Personality Psychology
description: An intensive examination of selected issues and research problems in personality psychology. The specific content will vary from year to year.
prerequisites: PSYB30H3 and [(PSYB01H3) or (PSYB04H3) or PSYB70H3] and [ PSYB07H3 or STAB22H3 or STAB23H3] and PSYC35H3
